I try not to pay attention
to those things.

62
00:02:44.301 --> 00:02:46.842
I have to admit.
I wasn't such a fan of <i>Descent.</i>

63
00:02:46.843 --> 00:02:48.926
although. clearly.
the book didn't suffer

64
00:02:48.927 --> 00:02:51.175
